title: Man that dress shit is spook
body:
A dress that can appear as two entirely different color schemes because of the image being washed out to the point where your brain has to agree on either one or the other, and that's what you see, even if it isn't what the actual colors are.

For those of you who don't know, I'm talking about this:

http://swiked.tumblr.com/image/112166688660
